{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3811","heading":"Effect on other law","label":"3811 Effect on other law","identifier":"/us/usc/t31/s3811","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t31/stIII/ch38","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft31%2Fs3811","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":null,"label":"a","identifier":"/us/usc/t31/s3811/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t31/s3811","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft31%2Fs3811%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"This chapter does not diminish the responsibility of any agency to comply with the provisions of chapter 35 of title 44.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":null,"label":"b","identifier":"/us/usc/t31/s3811/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t31/s3811","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft31%2Fs3811%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"This chapter does not supersede the provisions of .section 3512 of title 44","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":null,"label":"c","identifier":"/us/usc/t31/s3811/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t31/s3811","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft31%2Fs3811%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For purposes of this section, the term “agency” has the same meaning as in .section 3502(1) of title 44","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
